Installation instruction

Patch the database : 
drop it and then add the content pdns.sql.bz2
Add a readonly user named
MYSQLu=pdns_ro
MYSQLdb=pdns
MYSQLh=127.0.0.1
With only write access on cryptotime table, ro elsewhere

Put the pdnsec.sh script in /usr/local/sbin (or anywhere else)

Place a daily cron
